cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper deals with the problem of semantic segmentation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also uses machine learning techniques such as logistic LASSO regression and linear regression, which fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper uses measures of dispersion for predicted pixel-wise class probability distributions, which could fall under the category of neural networks (cs.NE) or multimedia (cs.MM).
